cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with cross-lingual transfer learning approaches for sentence representations. Additionally, the use of neural networks and adversarial training techniques suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper's focus on sentence representations and the use of GANs for cross-lingual mapping could also make it relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
